">What can be done to improve the situ-</div><div class="t maae x5a h4 yeae ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ation of the husband and wife who are &quot;in-</div><div class="t m83e x5a h4 y105b ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">compatible&quot;? </div><div class="t ma2 x56 h4 y1404 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m414 x7b h4 ye81 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In view of the Christian&apos;s responsibil-</div><div class="t m537 x5a h4 y15c3 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ity to maintain and guard the purity of the </div><div class="t m7df x5a h4 y1ed4 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">relationships between men and women, </div><div class="t m3b5 x5a h4 y1423 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">what standards should be held on the </div><div class="t m32d x5a h4 yf51 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">modesty of dress? </div><div class="t m1546 x14 h13 y11eb ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sabbath school lessons in Braille are supplied free to the blind upon </div><div class="t m21a1 x14 h13 y14d0 ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">request. Address: The Christian Record Braille Foundation, Inc., 4444 </div><div class="t m827 x14 h13 y11ff ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">South 52d Street, Lincoln, Nebraska 68516. </div><div class="t m22f4 x52 h4 y1432 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">[ 27 </div><div class="t m86f x1c h2f y1432 ff4 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
